Plot:

Based on a light novel series written by [Gatou Shouji] and illustrated by [Nakajima Yuka]. [Kanie Seiya], a high school boy, is invited on a date in an amusement park by a mysterious beautiful transfer student named [Sento Isuzu]. He is introduced to [Ratifa], a real princess and the park`s manager, and is asked to be the acting manager of this "disappointing amusement park in the Tokyo suburbs".

Source: ANN
